
simple configuration for keeping vim configuration across different machines


some steps which might be necessary to type


to copy the hole thing 

    git clone git@github.com:skeept/dotvim.git


the following updates the local folders to the same in the rep:

    git pull git@github.com:skeept/dotvim.git


in linux if (not done yet) have to do the following

    ln -s ~/vimrc  ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc


on windows the symlinks don't always work well: 
    cp vimrc  ..\_vimrc
    cp gvimrc ..\_gvimrc
